---
// src/components/WhyChooseTucontSection.astro
---

<section class="py-24 px-4 bg-slate-900 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-900/20 via-slate-900 to-orange-900/20"></div>
  
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto relative z-10">
    <!-- Cabeçalho -->
    <div class="text-center mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 via-purple-400 to-orange-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          Por que escolhem a Tucont Integrativa?
        </span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-2xl text-slate-300 font-semibold">
        Porque também somos empreendedores, te entendemos!
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- 1º Bloco - Nosso Sonho Grande -->
    <div class="mb-24 relative">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
            Nosso Sonho Grande:
          </h3>
          <div class="text-xl text-slate-300 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
            <p>
              Contribuir o Brasil a chegar a <span class="text-orange-400 font-bold">50 milhões de PJs</span> e
              mudar a sociedade, pelo despertar do empreendedorismo e acesso às oportunidades.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex justify-center relative">
          <div class="text-center space-y-8">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-8">
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-orange-400 mb-2">21MM</div>
                <div class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Atual</div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex-1 relative">
                <div class="h-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 to-blue-400 rounded-full shadow-lg shadow-orange-400/50"></div>
                <!-- Ícone TrendingUp SVG -->
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-400 absolute -top-3 right-0 transform translate-x-4 filter drop-shadow-lg drop-shadow-blue-400/30" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h7m0 0v7m0-7l-8 8-4-4-6 6"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-2">50MM</div>
                <div class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Meta</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
              Pessoas Jurídicas no Brasil
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="absolute -bottom-12 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2">
        <div class="w-1 h-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-orange-400 to-purple-400 rounded-full shadow-lg shadow-orange-400/50 animate-pulse"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 2º Bloco - Temos experiência -->
    <div class="mb-24 relative">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1 flex justify-center relative">
          <div class="relative w-full h-96 max-w-md">
            <!-- Card background com efeitos de glass -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500/20 to-orange-500/20 rounded-2xl backdrop-blur-sm"></div>
            
            <!-- Imagem do Geraldo ocupando todo o card -->
            <div class="absolute inset-4">
              <div class="relative w-full h-full">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500/30 to-orange-500/30 rounded-xl blur-lg animate-pulse"></div>
                <img 
                  src="/src/images/page/geraldo.png" 
                  alt="Geraldo Oliveira" 
                  class="relative w-full h-full object-cover rounded-xl shadow-2xl"
                  style={{
                    boxShadow: '0 0 50px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4), 0 0 100px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.3)',
                    objectPosition: 'center 50%'
                  }}
                />
                <!-- Badge do nome -->
                <div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-orange-500 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full font-bold shadow-lg text-sm">
                  Geraldo Oliveira
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 space-y-6">
          <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
            Temos experiência
          </h3>
          <div class="text-xl text-slate-300 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
            <p>
              Depois de criar, inspirar e ajudar mais de <span class="text-blue-400 font-bold">30 negócios</span>, 
              tínhamos o dever de impactar e transformar mais empreendedores.
            </p>
            <p>
              Eu sou o <span class="text-orange-400 font-bold">Geraldo Oliveira</span>, jornadeando no empreendedorismo 
              com a Infoco, Iuptec, Iupcare e agora transformando o mercado com a <span class="text-blue-400 font-bold">Tucont!</span>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="absolute -bottom-12 right-1/3 transform translate-x-1/2">
        <div class="w-1 h-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-purple-400 to-blue-400 rounded-full shadow-lg shadow-purple-400/50 animate-pulse delay-500"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 3º Bloco - Somos Integrativos -->
    <div class="mb-16 relative">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
            Somos Integrativos, é <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-orange-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Você no Centro</span>
          </h3>
          <div class="text-xl text-slate-300 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
            <p>
              Enquanto a Contabilidade Tradicional é <span class="text-slate-400 italic">reativa e foca no Governo</span>.
            </p>
            <p>
              A Tucont Integrativa foca no seu negócio, utiliza tecnologia proprietária para integrar e fluir a rotina empresarial.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex justify-center relative">
          <div class="relative w-full h-96 max-w-md">
            
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500/20 to-orange-500/20 rounded-2xl backdrop-blur-sm"></div>
            
            <!-- Empreendedora no centro - imagem ocupando todo o card -->
            <div class="absolute inset-4">
              <div class="relative w-full h-full">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500/30 to-orange-500/30 rounded-xl blur-lg animate-pulse"></div>
                <img 
                  src="/src/images/page/persona1.png" 
                  alt="Empreendedora no centro" 
                  class="relative w-full h-full object-cover rounded-xl shadow-2xl"
                  style={{
                    boxShadow: '0 0 30px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4), 0 0 60px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.2)'
                  }}
                />
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Ícones orbitando - ajustados para orbitar a imagem maior -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="relative w-full h-full">
                
                <!-- Pessoas - esquerda -->
                <div class="absolute top-1/2 -left-8 transform -translate-y-1/2 flex flex-col items-center">
                  <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-purple-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-2xl shadow-blue-500/50 animate-bounce mb-2">
                    <!-- Ícone Users SVG -->
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div class="text-xs text-slate-300 font-medium">Pessoas</div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Educação - topo -->
                <div class="absolute -top-8 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 flex flex-col items-center">
                  <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-orange-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-2xl shadow-purple-500/50 animate-bounce delay-500 mb-2">
                    <!-- Ícone BookOpen SVG -->
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div class="text-xs text-slate-300 font-medium">Educação</div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Tecnologia - direita -->
                <div class="absolute top-1/2 -right-8 transform -translate-y-1/2 flex flex-col items-center">
                  <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-blue-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-2xl shadow-orange-500/50 animate-bounce delay-1000 mb-2">
                    <!-- Ícone Lightbulb SVG -->
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div class="text-xs text-slate-300 font-medium">Tecnologia</div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Linhas conectoras animadas - ajustadas para a nova posição -->
                <svg class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full" viewBox="0 0 320 384">
                  <defs>
                    <linearGradient id="flow1" x1="0%" y1="50%" x2="100%" y2="50%">
                      <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#3b82f6" stop-opacity="0.6" />
                      <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#8b5cf6" stop-opacity="0.6" />
                    </linearGradient>
                    <linearGradient id="flow2" x1="0%" y1="50%" x2="100%" y2="50%">
                      <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#8b5cf6" stop-opacity="0.6" />
                      <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#f97316" stop-opacity="0.6" />
                    </linearGradient>
                  </defs>
                  
                  <!-- Linha da esquerda para o centro -->
                  <path
                    d="M 24,192 Q 80,192 120,192"
                    stroke="url(#flow1)"
                    stroke-width="3"
                    fill="none"
                    class="animate-pulse"
                    filter="drop-shadow(0 0 8px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4))"
                  />
                  
                  <!-- Linha da direita para o centro -->
                  <path
                    d="M 200,192 Q 240,192 296,192"
                    stroke="url(#flow2)"
                    stroke-width="3"
                    fill="none"
                    class="animate-pulse delay-500"
                    filter="drop-shadow(0 0 8px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.4))"
                  />
                  
                  <!-- Linha do topo para o centro -->
                  <path
                    d="M 160,24 Q 160,80 160,120"
                    stroke="url(#flow1)"
                    stroke-width="3"
                    fill="none"
                    class="animate-pulse delay-1000"
                    filter="drop-shadow(0 0 8px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.4))"
                  />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <div class="text-center mt-16">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500/10 to-orange-500/10 rounded-3xl p-12 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gradient-to-r from-blue-500/20 to-orange-500/20">
        <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
          Pronto para <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-orange-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">transformar</span> seu negócio?
        </h3>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Junte-se aos negócios que já transformaram suas jornadas empreendedoras conosco. 
          Vamos construir o futuro juntos!
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
          <a 
            href="#"
            class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-orange-500 hover:from-blue-600 hover:to-orange-600 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full shadow-2xl shadow-blue-500/25 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-orange-500/25 inline-flex items-center"
          >
            Começar Agora
            <!-- Ícone ArrowRight SVG -->
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
          
          <a 
            href="#"
            class="border-2 border-slate-400 text-slate-300 hover:bg-slate-800 hover:text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 inline-block"
          >
            Falar com Especialista
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-8 flex items-center justify-center gap-8 text-sm text-slate-400">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-400 rounded-full"></div>
            <span>Sem compromisso</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-400 rounded-full"></div>
            <span>Consultoria gratuita</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-orange-400 rounded-full"></div>
            <span>Resultados garantidos</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style is:global>
  /* Adicionando animações necessárias */
  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0.5; }
  }
  .animate-pulse {
    animation: pulse 2s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.6, 1) infinite;
  }
  .animate-pulse.delay-500 {
    animation-delay: 500ms;
  }
  .animate-pulse.delay-1000 {
    animation-delay: 1000ms;
  }

  @keyframes bounce {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
  }
  .animate-bounce {
    animation: bounce 1.5s infinite;
  }
  .animate-bounce.delay-500 {
    animation-delay: 500ms;
  }
  .animate-bounce.delay-1000 {
    animation-delay: 1000ms;
  }
</style>